title: Andover /Anoka studio rental, includes utilities
posting_body: ['Andover, mother inlaw efficiency apartment, lower level of rambler, $790, Available around  9-1-22 to 10-1-22', '- located off Roundlake Blvd and about 161th, this is around 6-8 minutes north of Riverdale and anoka on Roundlake Blvd and Highway 10 , this is a rental for one person, the entrance shared with upstairs apartment, ( the entrance will be seperated in the next 8 weeks, this will be un-furnished, has its own kitchen, bathroom,', '- Includes utilities and internet, Initial 10 month lease.', '- Rental requirements, first, last month rent along with damage deposit,  references, proof of income, background/credit check processed, rental references.', 'proccessing fee $50', '- If you have a serious interest in the apartment you can email me relevant rental info about yourself.', '*', 'First and last Name.', '* How many in household.', '* Do you Have rental references.', '* Do you have pets, type.', '* Do you have at least 3 times monthly rent as income.', '-Will not be able to show apartment till sometime in August.', "-If this is posted it's available.", '-I will be getting back to applicants over the next several weeks.', 'Anoka Coon Rapids Blaine Oak Grove , East Bethel Cedar , St Francis Ramsey']
